---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/hss-phase1.css';
---

<Layout title="Custom Wedding Stationery Requests | Hummingbird Social Studio" description="Request a custom wedding invitation, signage piece, or matching stationery item from Hummingbird Social Studio.">
  <main class="hss-page">
    <section class="hss-hero"><div class="hss-container"><p class="hss-eyebrow">Custom Requests</p><h1>Need a custom piece that still feels like Hummingbird?</h1><p class="hss-lead">If you love the studio style but need a custom layout, matching suite piece, signage item, or wording support, send a quick note with what you are looking for.</p><div class="hss-button-row"><a class="hss-button" href="mailto:gradualgrowthonline@gmail.com?subject=Custom%20Wedding%20Stationery%20Request">Email a Custom Request</a><a class="hss-button-secondary" href="/shop/">Shop Templates</a></div></div></section>
    <section class="hss-section"><div class="hss-container hss-grid"><article class="hss-card"><h2>Matching suite pieces</h2><p>Request a coordinating RSVP card, details card, menu, welcome sign, seating chart, table number, thank you card, or bar sign.</p></article><article class="hss-card"><h2>Custom wording help</h2><p>Get help with wording for adult-only events, welcome parties, micro-weddings, elopement announcements, or unique family situations.</p></article><article class="hss-card"><h2>Event-specific layouts</h2><p>Request a design adjusted for rehearsal dinners, bridal showers, welcome parties, post-elopement celebrations, or intimate weddings.</p></article></div></section>
    <section class="hss-section"><div class="hss-narrow"><p class="hss-eyebrow">What to Include</p><h2>Send the details that make the request easy to quote.</h2><ul class="hss-list"><li>The product or design style you like</li><li>The type of piece you need</li><li>Your event date or ideal timeline</li><li>Any wording, size, or printing requirements</li><li>Whether you need one piece or a full suite</li></ul><p class="hss-mini-note">You can replace this email CTA with a form later through your preferred form tool.</p></div></section>
  </main>
</Layout>
